Experience
Bank of France | Economist & Statistician | Dec 2020 – present

Monthly publication of the evolution of economic activity in New Aquitaine, based on data collected by the Banque de France,
Collection of monthly turnover figures from traders in Nouvelle-Aquitaine for the national publication of Retail Trade, using tools developed internally in VBA,
Creation of monthly economic dashboards for the visualization of data from the New Aquitaine region. Created with PowerPoint, it supports presentations in regional authorities and consular chambers.

ESSCA | Lecturer | Jan 2024 – present

Animation des cours d’analyse financières et stratégie d’investissement auprès des élèves de Master ;
Création du syllabus ainsi que tous les supports de cour ;

